verbose_text: Quantitative real-time PCR (qPCR) analysis of eyes of I-10 mice revealed that Dz13 inhibited the OIR inducible expression of not only c-jun mRNA relative to Dz13scr, but also that of FGF-2, VEGF-A, VEGF-C, MMP-2, MMP-9, MMP-12 and MMP-13 (XREF_FIG).
evidence: expression of not only c-jun mRNA
